{
  "stem": "15082.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very good in math.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was my strongest point in school, always.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I could just see it, what they were doing to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, when I look back, they were just-- no matter what I did, I was always wrong.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Geometry I was good at.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it just didn't suit them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they could that what they will.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's not like you could go to the Board of Education and complain, and that they ran the school, period.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had the final say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, really, just coming home complaining was all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But even then, I realized there was very little they could do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just kept plugging, and sticking with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My dad always says, just stick with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's the best we can do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It frustrated me to a point, where maybe at times [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I felt that my hard work and everything is to null, because you aim for marks.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but I realized that the alternative would be, you can't get out of school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was compulsory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you might as well stick with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As time went on, the only fear that we had is getting beaten up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it became a part of life, that you just accepted it, going home from school, and every once in a while, getting punched out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was no way of fighting back, because you were outnumbered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you took your lickings, and you went home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am not one that cries easy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hurt inside a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I do not cry a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Remember ?] a few of them that are-- there's only two that are left from my time that were in my class.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
